latestIgtvVideos.title: FUH, Medical Excellence. Now in UAE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@fakeehuniversityhospital brought to the UAE by pioneering Saudi healthcare provider group, Fakeeh Care with a rich legacy of over 43 years, committed to delivering medical excellence and championing outstanding research in the UAE. Located in @dubaisiliconoasis , FUH is a 350-bed state of the art facility, set to provide primary, secondary and tertiary care to an estimated 700,000 patients a year. equipped with cutting-edge technology and smart systems that are built to meet the unique needs of the hospital & UAE patients.
FUH uses innovative diagnostic technology, advanced data-assisted & automated medication dispensing systems, which combined with leading medical expertise, make patient diagnoses, care precise and efficient.
Operating as a teaching hospital in Dubai, FUH will provide world-class medical education to the future generations of doctors in the UAE, expanding the medical horizons of practicing healthcare experts, while also bringing the latest research to its patients.
The hospital will be a benchmark for medical collaboration, international affiliations and will combine medical education in a modern environment.
Quick facts about FUH;
*Largest healthcare investment in the UAE: USD 500 million
*Facility size: 1 million square feet
*Hospital capacity: 350 beds
*Estimated annual care capacity: 700,000 patients/ year
*The facility is comprised of a 4-story structure with 2 basements
*Number of specialized clinics within the hospital: 55 clinics
*Number of operating rooms: 13 ORs, including one entirely dedicated to emergency obstetrics
care
*Intensive care units: 35 adult ICUs, 10 paediatric ICUs and 15 neonatal ICUs
*FUH has the largest emergency department in Dubai, spread across 35,000 square feet with 12 examination rooms, 18 short stay beds, 4 nursing
stations, 4 resuscitation stations, and 4 triage rooms
*Specialty departments inclusive of: 20 dialysis stations, 8 water birthing centres, a hyperbaric
chamber, a sleep lab, a fully equipped rehabilitation department with gym, hydrotherapy pool, patient central monitoring, a fully automated laboratory, a full range diagnostics & imaging department
*Fully automated pharmacy with robots
